# Machines accessed via ProxyJump through earth
Host sneezy-earth
    User melashri
    HostName sneezy.geop.uc.edu
    Port 22
    ProxyJump melashri@earth.phy.uc.edu:22
    LocalForward 31417 localhost:31417
    PubkeyAuthentication no
    PasswordAuthentication yes
    PreferredAuthentications password
    IdentitiesOnly yes
    IdentityAgent none
    ForwardAgent yes
    ForwardX11 yes
    ForwardX11Trusted yes
    ServerAliveInterval 600
    ServerAliveCountMax 240

Host sleepy-earth
    User melashri
    HostName sleepy.geop.uc.edu
    Port 22
    ProxyJump melashri@earth.phy.uc.edu:22
    LocalForward 31418 localhost:31418
    PubkeyAuthentication no
    PasswordAuthentication yes
    PreferredAuthentications password
    IdentitiesOnly yes
    IdentityAgent none
    ForwardAgent yes
    ForwardX11 yes
    ForwardX11Trusted yes
    ServerAliveInterval 600
    ServerAliveCountMax 240

Host goofy-earth
